        <code>/api/vehicle/gasrecords</code>
    </div>
    <div class="col-3">
        Returns a list of gas records for the vehicle
    </div>
    <div class="col-3">
        vehicleId - Id of Vehicle
        <br />
        useMPG(bool) - Use Imperial Units and Calculation
        <br />
        useUKMPG(bool) - Use UK Imperial Calculation
    </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-1">
